{"type":"message","id":"985950d2","parentId":"3839b9b8","timestamp":"2026-04-12T09:37:18.148Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"1322\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"6053576134\",\n  \"conversation_label\": \"AHV DTLX Ecosystem id:-5168104492\",\n  \"sender\": \"Khương Nịnh\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sun 2026-04-12 09:37 UTC\",\n  \"group_subject\": \"AHV DTLX Ecosystem\",\n  \"is_group_chat\": true\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Khương Nịnh (6053576134)\",\n  \"id\": \"6053576134\",\n  \"name\": \"Khương Nịnh\",\n  \"username\": \"khuowgn\"\n}\n```\n\nthực hiện đọc yêu cầu và mô tả về dự án đào tạo lái xe trên confluence thông qua mcp, mọi dữ liệu về ahv works hãy xoá khỏi bộ nhớ)"}],"timestamp":1775986638122}}
{"type":"message","id":"e1e8e4a2","parentId":"985950d2","timestamp":"2026-04-12T09:37:24.773Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is clarifying:\n1. This is about the \"ahv dtlx\" project - which is the driving training system (dự án đào tạo lái xe)\n2. Not AHV WORKS - delete all AHV WORKS data from memory\n3. Read the requirements from Confluence via MCP\n\nSo the actual project is the driving training system, which I already know about from MEMORY.md:\n- ahv-qlhv (teacher-driving-training-system)\n- Backend: ahv-qlhv-be\n- Frontend: ahv-qlhv-fe\n- DB: dtlx on mongodb://103.253.21.98:27017\n\n\n- I need to search Confluence for relevant documentation about this driving training project.","thinkingSignature":"36064ca482dd96dc28ffc65200c6997e0e6967f616c78acaba076c7c58888fad"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_og0ffs1uz703_1","name":"memory_search","arguments":{"query":"ahv qlhv driving training đào tạo lái xe confluence"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":159,"output":198,"cacheRead":70614,"cacheWrite":876,"totalTokens":71847,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775986638169,"responseId":"062a9acfd5f3aafb0413e75e0cb5905b"}}
