{"type":"message","id":"507fd92e","parentId":"8bbf8d9c","timestamp":"2026-04-12T09:38:22.264Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see the QLHV project commits. Let me also try to get the README content through the gitlab tool differently, or look at branches and pipelines. Also let me check the merge requests on the BE repo to get more context.\n\nThe key finding is: the Confluence space \"AW\" only has AHV WORKS docs, no QLHV driving training docs. The user said to read from Confluence via MCP, but there's nothing there about the driving training project. \n\nLet me try a few more searches in Confluence to be thorough - maybe the space key is different.","thinkingSignature":"5fa603d49dd304792327f819339243b893f9125825bd73216bdd07ca25864994"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_hjwmcpdtlo1g_1","name":"confluence__confluence_search_pages","arguments":{"query":"teacher","limit":20}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_hjwmcpdtlo1g_2","name":"confluence__confluence_search_pages","arguments":{"query":"học viên","limit":20}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_hjwmcpdtlo1g_3","name":"confluence__confluence_search_pages","arguments":{"query":"driving","limit":20}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":1842,"output":235,"cacheRead":78431,"cacheWrite":832,"totalTokens":81340,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775986693500,"responseId":"062a9b06939b8d682b7989c16ad819ab"}}
