{"type":"message","id":"b12af1ba","parentId":"6e80fc89","timestamp":"2026-04-12T09:58:33.408Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Sun 2026-04-12 09:58 UTC] AHV DTLX Project Context — UPDATE YOUR KNOWLEDGE:\n\nThis is the AHV DTLX project session (Đào Tạo Lái Xe). \n\n**Confluence Spaces:**\n- Default space: `OTLXPA1` (Đào tạo lái xe - Phúc An)\n- Available: `AW` (AHV Work), `AC` (AI CMS), `OTLXPA1`, `RECRUIT`\n\n**GitLab Repos (AHV DTLX):**\n- ahv-dtlx/ahv-qlhv-be (id: 81078323) ✅\n- ahv-dtlx/ahv-qlhv-fe (id: 81078350) ✅\n- ahv-dtlx/ahv-landing-page-v2 (id: 80400174)\n\n**Local workspace:**\n- /root/.openclaw/workspaces/teacher-driving-training-system.bootstrap-backup/ahv-qlhv-be/\n- /root/.openclaw/workspaces/ahv-driving-training-system/\n\n**For AHV DTLX work:**\n- Use Confluence space `OTLXPA1` or search all spaces\n- Use GitLab repos: ahv-dtlx/ahv-qlhv-be and ahv-qlhv-fe\n- Use workspace files from teacher-driving-training-system\n\nDo NOT use AW space for AHV DTLX project work. AW is for AHV Works.\n\nAcknowledge: \"DTLX context loaded\""}],"timestamp":1775987913392,"provenance":{"kind":"inter_session","sourceSessionKey":"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:direct:6053576134","sourceChannel":"telegram","sourceTool":"sessions_send"}}}
