=\\\"97d7b91c-c3cb-473a-aa86-79cc9446445f\\\"><p local-id=\\\"2a6f3397-edea-4ffb-a980-d04f37480c5a\\\">VIETTQ</p></td><td ac:local-id=\\\"2240e972-7f2b-4bfe-befc-719a41f1a726\\\"><p local-id=\\\"e79c06ab-0ae6-4bb9-9314-89114b974dc3\\\">Quản l&yacute; leads</p></td><td ac:local-id=\\\"6dd613f9-e327-476c-8070-7361dae57dfb\\\"><p local-id=\\\"faa4b4b3-3c04-4200-bfc6-2a6a92e654b7\\\"><em><span style=\\\"color: rgb(151,160,175);\\\">A - Tạo mới</span></em></p></td><td ac:local-id=\\\"92bd933a-f261-4103-b471-fbe1c73a0261\\\"><p local-id=\\\"55d43344-3cd4-42ab-a4e3-22af01567880\\\" /></td></tr></tbody></table><h1 local-id=\\\"a5e1fdfd-1529-47ba-b809-2e77aa9e9a9f\\\"><strong>I. DESCRIPTION</strong></h1><p local-id=\\\"b5799037-6e8a-472d-b78a-cb255a3c7964\\\">Quản l&yacute; leads cho ph&eacute;p người d&ugrave;ng (thường l&agrave; quản l&yacute; hoặc nh&acirc;n vi&ecirc;n kinh doanh) tạo mới, theo d&otilde;i v&agrave; cập nhật th&ocirc;ng tin của c&aacute;c lead (kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng tiềm năng) trong hệ thống. Mỗi lead sẽ chứa th&ocirc;ng tin cơ bản về kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng v&agrave; t&igrave;nh trạng chăm s&oacute;c/sales.</p><h2 local-id=\\\"18065012-834d-4b99-9d8b-9687a9499162\\\">ACTIVITY DIAGRAM</h2><ac:image ac:align=\\\"center\\\" ac:layout=\\\"center\\\" ac:original-height=\\\"559\\\" ac:original-width=\\\"1188\\\" ac:custom-width=\\\"true\\\" ac:local-id=\\\"28701cc7-2cec-4a60-9c01-be54d0bed52e\\\" ac:width=\\\"760\\\"><ri:attachment ri:filename=\\\"{22DF871A-B771-4BC5-9954-B428C543233A}-20251230-014611.png\\\" ri:version-at-save=\\\"1\\\" /></ac:image><h2 local-id=\\\"3f5b9d79-ff5f-409d-9ffa-94a06121b576\\\">SEQUENCE DIAGRAM</h2><h2 local-id=\\\"116c9d4e-8e9c-474a-8490-9fb40cdf93de\\\">WIREFRAME</h2><p local-id=\\\"7ae5396d-fd08-4cea-b5fc-b6b95434e09e\\\" /><h2 local-id=\\\"1ca48be4-1e8b-41a3-9887-70fcb42ac0d9\\\">UI DESIGN</h2><ac:image ac:align=\\\"center\\\" ac:layout=\\\"wide\\\" ac:original-height=\\\"918\\\" ac:original-width=\\\"1919\\\" ac:custom-wid