"><p local-id=\\\"682001a5-10b1-4ef3-bd42-9d2e354abe50\\\">-</p></td><td ac:local-id=\\\"fab3dd4d-1173-4206-81ad-413cf3af4b90\\\"><p local-id=\\\"18c7c7ee-9551-4765-b4aa-1c4c2bd0df6c\\\">-</p></td><td ac:local-id=\\\"807e274d-e466-4a7d-97dd-205da44af91a\\\"><p local-id=\\\"ce6d5e66-9f6a-4297-98f7-7b347af61a25\\\">Học vi&ecirc;n đ&atilde; học ở trung t&acirc;m quan t&acirc;m đến kh&oacute;a học kh&aacute;c cũng c&oacute; thể trở th&agrave;nh kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng tiềm năng</p><p local-id=\\\"758fcdff-1098-4718-9baf-6e520904bd32\\\"><strong>Default value:</strong></p><p local-id=\\\"eeb14126-eb6d-47c7-8d92-7b52f98619a5\\\">Hint text hiển thị &ldquo;Chọn học vi&ecirc;n&rdquo;</p><p local-id=\\\"6598c1a7-b93b-4f06-8d5d-562993684d5e\\\"><strong>OnClick:</strong></p><p local-id=\\\"78a53bcd-0866-4188-a3a9-12a45d2952de\\\">Hiển thị danh s&aacute;ch c&aacute;c học vi&ecirc;n c&oacute; trong cơ sở dữ liệu dạng dropdown &rarr; Click chọn học vi&ecirc;n &rarr; Tự động cập nhật c&aacute;c trường dữ liệu th&ocirc;ng tin đ&atilde; lưu trữ của học vi&ecirc;n lưu trong cơ sở dữ liệu</p></td></tr><tr ac:local-id=\\\"d782a3d7-e438-4a22-9ada-78d4871ae3db\\\"><td ac:local-id=\\\"f1e58349-c1c2-4b84-83b8-0dcbfad3aed7\\\"><p local-id=\\\"a6b5a5c8-4619-4803-8e5e-0aae8438ddea\\\">Họ t&ecirc;n</p></td><td ac:local-id=\\\"2600064b-6295-4336-b429-baec6f92bc1e\\\"><p local-id=\\\"c957a226-3456-4e7a-bf85-8a876a42f650\\\">Textbox</p></td><td ac:local-id=\\\"aaf6349a-179c-46e9-bf0e-bcc782fff31a\\\"><p local-id=\\\"a14562dd-d5bc-48a4-aaba-ca8a583dea75\\\">Text</p></td><td ac:local-id=\\\"9c239b7f-d12c-4399-8659-73437a359ac1\\\"><p local-id=\\\"238ddf43-b730-4d33-97ac-166b59f36993\\\">Y</p></td><td ac:local-id=\\\"a49c9672-8c4e-415c-a1d1-c3b616c7e9b2\\\"><p local-id=\\\"ebd8f08f-4d13-41f3-9ac2-efeb04fa730c\\\">-</p></td><td ac:local-id=\\\"ebe22c53-b909-4a8d-b6bf-8332f689ef63\\\"><p local-id=\\\"b6780db1-0f1e-46f9-99e5-e7524adbd0c7\\\"><strong>OnClick:</strong></p><p local-id=\\\"07f3cd5c-9d98-46f2-818c-895baa04b4dc\\\">Nhập họ t&ecirc;n kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng tiềm năng</p><p local-id=\\\"8311664d-beac-4467-80a1-82a010408f55\\\"><strong>Require: </strong></p><p local-id=\\\"a4b0ae82-3ed0-4f31-9755-f9d8af1540a3\\\">Kh&ocirc;ng để trống trường &ldquo;Họ t&ecirc;n&rdquo;</p><ul local-id=\\\"747c291b-7db9-4684-a405-e1ed6864e04c\\\"><li local-id=\\\"6c9c3627-fc85-4bb2-8e2f-397ba6b3bcba\\\"><p local-id=\\\"0c3b1ac6-4c3c-4ddc-a2da-7467a29902c5\\\">Để trống &rarr; Click\n\n⚠️ [... middle content omitted — showing head and tail ...]\n\nuo; &rarr; Gửi y&ecirc;u cầu đến server</p></li></ul><ac:image ac:align=\\\"center\\\" ac:layout=\\\"center\\\" ac:original-height=\\\"38\\\" ac:original-width=\\\"47\\\" ac:custom-width=\\\"true\\\" ac:local-id=\\\"bc38f231-7e8f-45ba-9cad-0a80fc220473\\\" ac:alt=\\\"image-20250731-014248.png\\\" ac:width=\\\"47\\\"><ri:attachment ri:filename=\\\"image-20250731-014248.png\\\" ri:version-at-save=\\\"1\\\" /></ac:image><p local-id=\\\"30ee0f00-de37-4f30-8c43-9671b6ddc725\\\" /></td></tr><tr ac:local-id=\\\"792647f7-b1da-4c6d-b72e-6c685aedf44d\\\"><td ac:local-id=\\\"a8f70dff-1ca8-49a2-b740-201833eb0948\\\"><p local-id=\\\"81168a6e-d6f5-4256-a3ef-1224f0d84db5\\\">Server</p></td><td ac:local-id=\\\"cfdc8f9c-e5b8-4d3c-bbc2-5b63b3554901\\\"><p local-id=\\\"189c68ce-351a-4ec3-9142-8ea1f1db4983\\\">Nhận y&ecirc;u cầu, x&oacute;a dữ liệu của kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng đ&oacute; trong database, gửi th&ocirc;ng b&aacute;o ra client</p></td></tr><tr ac:local-id=\\\"0c532e3f-b4c2-49ba-b6ea-e2bdc1a71143\\\"><td ac:local-id=\\\"8f8c8578-6adb-4bd9-9784-6cb265febff4\\\"><p local-id=\\\"5d57c552-19d2-41c1-b3c6-da792622165f\\\">Client</p></td><td ac:local-id=\\\"9646ba17-e575-4e12-bdfb-ead77a20bc78\\\"><p local-id=\\\"f8846739-32a5-4d4b-bdbe-b5b8c95948d1\\\">Hiển thị th&ocirc;ng b&aacute;o &ldquo;X&oacute;a kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng tiềm năng th&agrave;nh c&ocirc;ng&rdquo;, cập nhật lại danh s&aacute;ch leads </p></td></tr></tbody></table><h2 local-id=\\\"88c4d59c-49d5-45f9-ae59-5669c2745dca\\\">AC3, L&agrave; một admin/sale t&ocirc;i muốn m&igrave;nh c&oacute; thể th&ecirc;m lịch l&agrave;m việc với kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng tiềm năng</h2><table data-table-width=\\\"760\\\" data-layout=\\\"default\\\" ac:local-id=\\\"8eb8aad9-343e-439c-8640-797e225aba1c\\\"><tbody><tr ac:local-id=\\\"6cd44fb7-a0c1-46fc-b332-4b596ad79129\\\"><th ac:local-id=\\\"4be485fe-7f81-4262-b9be-ecbd504ae253\\\"><p local-id=\\\"b4740e77-7e68-4670-bd6e-51ca2ae86e41\\\"><strong>Scenario</strong></p></th><th ac:local-id=\\\"95425b2f-e326-4e5a-8ae5-c1048848d062\\\"><p local-id=\\\"5dbadeae-ee12-41ec-a656-e28c13298a5b\\\"><strong>T&aacute;c nh&acirc;n</strong></p></th><th ac:local-id=\\\"ea7199f1-ea9a-44e8-a5db-96cff18a5dc1\\\"><p local-id=\\\"b8b54d7e-262e-4b6f-8074-723dafc88f80\\\"><strong>Kết quả</strong></p></th></tr><tr ac:local-id=\\\"9f2ee6f3-9d6c-45cb-b4ec-4c7e147cbde9\\\"><td rowspan=\\\"3\\\" ac:local-id=\\\"8adf0ee2-79bd-4804-9894-0d75f1a138fc\\\"><p local-id=\\\"7b2c5a9a-d985-403e-8b71-7ca30023d95c\\\">Admin/sale c&oacute; thể th&ecirc;m lịch l&agrave;m việc với kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng tiềm năng</p></td><td ac:local-id=\\\"1e611570-fda1-46e7-94bc-375a4700edbc\\\"><p local-id=\\\"5f2219c1-ea32-4fa5-9670-8917478f19e7\\\">Client</p></td><td ac:local-id=\\\"c26e028d-c227-4e98-9795-692ac0e710a5\\\"><p local-id=\\\"cc29ac00-1525-4668-b10f-5626af3a9d0f\\\">M&agrave;n sửa kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng tiềm năng, click &ldquo;C&ocirc;ng việc&rdquo;/&rdquo;Lịch họp&rdquo;/&rdquo;Lịch gọi&rdquo; &rarr; Hiển thị popup th&ecirc;m c&ocirc;ng việc/lịch họp/lịch gọi &rarr; Nhập th&ocirc;ng tin v&agrave; lưu</p></td></tr><tr ac:local-id=\\\"e4b89beb-3d6d-4f85-b80a-3d3c600933b0\\\"><td ac:local-id=\\\"439b10f2-bda8-4c1e-b299-da452c10220b\\\"><p local-id=\\\"d592c548-9d8e-4d5b-85a7-79b3145c8bdb\\\">Server</p></td><td ac:local-id=\\\"465fe8b7-47cf-4af4-a293-5872c76fedac\\\"><p local-id=\\\"31a742c5-b2dc-44f3-8626-753afefa5c58\\\">Validate, cập nhật dữ liệu v&agrave; trả kết quả ra client</p></td></tr><tr ac:local-id=\\\"002b101a-5bec-421b-95bf-124cb14c2503\\\"><td ac:local-id=\\\"b8674d63-6bd1-4307-9ed1-fc5063e927b4\\\"><p local-id=\\\"abe0c01b-6efe-4d62-8189-81d2ab3ee104\\\">Client</p></td><td ac:local-id=\\\"09df95d6-26be-4681-9792-ca7a782aa8a8\\\"><p local-id=\\\"10ef9089-c69f-4830-8592-1fe41c4eb5d0\\\">TH1: Thất bại &rarr; Highlight v&agrave; hiển thị th&ocirc;ng b&aacute;o c&aacute;c trường lỗi</p><p local-id=\\\"8b3b3275-9949-4725-b314-05a49c4340ee\\\">TH2: Th&agrave;nh c&ocirc;ng &rarr; Đ&oacute;ng popup, hiển thị th&ocirc;ng b&aacute;o &ldquo;Th&ecirc;m lịch th&agrave;nh c&ocirc;ng&rdquo; v&agrave; dữ liệu lịch mới th&ecirc;m ở bảng lịch l&agrave;m việc</p></td></tr></tbody></table>\"\n}[... 80064 more characters truncated]"}],"details":{"mcpServer":"confluence","mcpTool":"confluence_get_page"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775988827511}}
