local-id=\\\"2f10a4c5-f533-49ad-902f-8f1d4d8ff69a\\\">Highlight ng&agrave;y hiện tại</p></li></ul><p local-id=\\\"d9344b5e-b614-4aeb-a79d-8d7ce8350bfc\\\"><strong>Default value:</strong></p><p local-id=\\\"657c3fb6-158f-448c-a482-13e3fef6aab6\\\">Hint text hiển thị &ldquo;dd/mm/yyyy&rdquo;</p><p local-id=\\\"061b722f-467c-4b9a-8c19-6f3ccec6cb6d\\\"><strong>OnClick:</strong></p><p local-id=\\\"b074c854-73cb-4ffe-b0db-5d7\n\n⚠️ [... middle content omitted — showing head and tail ...]\n\nd5-9001-02b03dc598a6\\\"><p local-id=\\\"e5b3eb66-6fb4-4185-826b-a3082df66630\\\">L&agrave; một admin t&ocirc;i muốn m&igrave;nh c&oacute; thể th&ecirc;m mới học vi&ecirc;n</p></li><li local-id=\\\"5b45fed3-4c04-4162-86c2-8d3e66270401\\\"><p local-id=\\\"6c693f0e-9ec2-4d6c-8c5f-7610d64932d4\\\">L&agrave; một admin t&ocirc;i muốn m&igrave;nh c&oacute; thể sửa/x&oacute;a th&ocirc;ng tin của học vi&ecirc;n</p></li></ul><h2 local-id=\\\"bb59bad3-b771-493a-8190-918d49dd4e16\\\">PRE-CONDITION</h2><p local-id=\\\"e3e8ab3c-0989-4655-9e1e-523fa457522b\\\">Người d&ugrave;ng cần c&oacute; t&agrave;i khoản ĐTLX đ&atilde; được cấp ph&eacute;p theo role admin</p><h2 local-id=\\\"477b9182-cd06-4303-bbc6-e674fe8092de\\\">ACCEPTANCE CRITERIA</h2><h2 local-id=\\\"b117bcf6-91c8-49a0-a2a0-870c3119326a\\\">AC1, L&agrave; một admin t&ocirc;i muốn m&igrave;nh c&oacute; thể th&ecirc;m mới học vi&ecirc;n</h2><table data-table-width=\\\"760\\\" data-layout=\\\"default\\\" ac:local-id=\\\"0add8156-e95f-44b7-a274-be69654f1f85\\\"><tbody><tr ac:local-id=\\\"dfbf69b5-bc21-493d-9435-e148f70e17ef\\\"><th ac:local-id=\\\"30bea4a7-8e65-4456-8313-bcb614392d20\\\"><p local-id=\\\"d3198339-7c37-4349-a95a-380094bb884c\\\"><strong>Scenario</strong></p></th><th ac:local-id=\\\"7ce3645f-3ed3-4938-ad72-faf07de6abec\\\"><p local-id=\\\"0d9ffec7-e4eb-4ebd-8c57-403ed0961fe1\\\"><strong>T&aacute;c nh&acirc;n</strong></p></th><th ac:local-id=\\\"43387e39-95bf-4b12-83f8-1e48354f6a89\\\"><p local-id=\\\"0b35dbbe-f36f-425e-851f-bfb90df42b5d\\\"><strong>Kết quả</strong></p></th></tr><tr ac:local-id=\\\"c3618dbd-2096-49f9-8d25-9ef26e88cd5d\\\"><td rowspan=\\\"4\\\" ac:local-id=\\\"7a47af4a-4bd2-4d9f-80c8-465a3aea8897\\\"><p local-id=\\\"6117c4e7-a6b5-4101-afb4-a84adfc3e428\\\">Admin c&oacute; thể th&ecirc;m mới học vi&ecirc;n</p></td><td ac:local-id=\\\"5be883eb-9209-4b72-95b6-aef06935186e\\\"><p local-id=\\\"d2c0aafa-076e-4549-8e10-8beae139b994\\\">Client</p></td><td ac:local-id=\\\"8343c8be-9e98-49f0-962e-8bb8e8f4f05e\\\"><p local-id=\\\"d842596d-0306-4e69-8e85-f698be36cf06\\\">M&agrave;n &ldquo;Danh s&aacute;ch gi&aacute;o vi&ecirc;n&rdquo;, click button &ldquo;Th&ecirc;m gi&aacute;o vi&ecirc;n mới&rdquo;</p></td></tr><tr ac:local-id=\\\"2c2ec8e2-1a24-42a8-b345-b6e86abd8a57\\\"><td ac:local-id=\\\"e4a96aa4-39eb-4890-954f-a2db00feca5a\\\"><p local-id=\\\"41f9363c-50bf-4b55-99a9-a95e7947e463\\\">Client</p></td><td ac:local-id=\\\"7424a626-76e1-4ebf-88ce-f8aa4d71cc26\\\"><p local-id=\\\"3235cce6-58e1-4e50-a014-aee33a6c9f68\\\">Chuyển hướng đến trang &ldquo;Th&ecirc;m mới gi&aacute;o vi&ecirc;n&rdquo;, nhập th&ocirc;ng tin</p><ul local-id=\\\"c96d5b85-2945-484e-a821-70cea222f7b1\\\"><li local-id=\\\"d0f35b95-93e7-45c3-b614-704e80e4802b\\\"><p local-id=\\\"a792b8f6-6d9f-402a-80d0-9962a4145914\\\">TH1: Click button &ldquo;Quay lại&rdquo; &rarr; Chuyển hướng về trang &ldquo;Danh s&aacute;ch gi&aacute;o vi&ecirc;n&rdquo;</p></li><li local-id=\\\"9152f99f-45c8-4d84-9a84-9235fc537532\\\"><p local-id=\\\"d3f20e4b-cfd0-4de4-9e47-e423bd5d05f5\\\">TH2: Click button &ldquo;Lưu&rdquo; &rarr; Gửi y&ecirc;u cầu đến server </p></li></ul></td></tr><tr ac:local-id=\\\"bb42ddb3-8122-4dc9-93c8-3958862b730e\\\"><td ac:local-id=\\\"b5f07986-679a-4ed2-ac61-bc7988960e41\\\"><p local-id=\\\"2ea4494b-d43c-4ae3-873a-580acd8eb216\\\">Server</p></td><td ac:local-id=\\\"1b4c67f0-13a4-4c3d-a918-c8c87ecea60d\\\"><p local-id=\\\"0ff870ff-81e3-46b4-82bc-bf09691a2e70\\\">Validate, cập nhật dữ liệu v&agrave; trả kết quả ra client</p></td></tr><tr ac:local-id=\\\"7c6f202c-c4d4-4669-961f-9d8f7ddb8cdb\\\"><td ac:local-id=\\\"5b5d7a13-e53a-4ae8-9ad8-e8615675ed31\\\"><p local-id=\\\"9e3ba2aa-364f-4fb0-907c-c3faced1d571\\\">Client</p></td><td ac:local-id=\\\"5f35ff7f-f302-4022-828b-8c428b7f3f4a\\\"><p local-id=\\\"d9d5e412-988c-445d-a107-7eaf7a9f0af2\\\">TH1: Thất bại &rarr; Highlight hiển thị th&ocirc;ng b&aacute;o trường lỗi</p><p local-id=\\\"f90fdee3-f2a7-41af-91ae-b6037c30e6f0\\\">TH2: Th&agrave;nh c&ocirc;ng &rarr; Chuyển hướng, cập nhật dữ liệu &ldquo;Danh s&aacute;ch gi&aacute;o vi&ecirc;n&rdquo; v&agrave; hiển thị th&ocirc;ng b&aacute;o th&agrave;nh c&ocirc;ng</p></td></tr></tbody></table>\"\n}[... 51861 more characters truncated]"}],"details":{"mcpServer":"confluence","mcpTool":"confluence_get_page"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775988827526}}
